{"tid":712613,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"點解老一輩咁中意人地同佢講生日快樂","createTime":"2018-06-22T08:17:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-22T11:44:00.000Z","uid":172607,"like":3,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1f0b32d0ea94f5b688b39785a5d8edd527a6bc11","tid":712613,"uid":172607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T08:17:11.000Z","msg":"公司有個老屎忽做左好多年<br />\n無啦啦請大家食cake<br />\n人地問咩事咁開心呀<br />\n佢話：今日我生日呀 所以好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n老公同我去邊度邊度慶祝.......<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大家即刻講 生日快樂等等客氣說話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實佢唔講根本唔會有人知佢生日<br />\n特登買cake 請大家食<br />\n然後暗示自己今日生日<br />\n想人地同佢講生日快樂其實係咩心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同岩布仙尼happy birthday to me有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真心on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce6049967cfcb292fcc062088fa711b9d2ee5c84","tid":712613,"uid":172607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T08:17:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67e9d202792f62147a81fd3bd660cf3f805ba80a","tid":712613,"uid":120715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T08:19:52.000Z","msg":"因為人生冇幾多年再有得慶祝"},{"pid":"3c6085cf4da51407c947269e65753d93aa991cfd","tid":712613,"uid":181819,"like":0,"dislike":